stylometry: Data mining is a method used for looking for trends in data. It is important in businesses because it allows you to cluster items/people of similar characteristics, look for sequences, and look for associations. Data mining may help a business determine certain trends and may help determine who a company's target market is based on clusters. It can also help a bank when looking at its customers. For instance, it can find sequences in data, such as trends in different loans that customers take out.
